lead_paragraph: Jared Goff showed up to the UC Irvine dorms a bit ahead of his fellow rookies Tuesday, getting a quick start on his first training camp with the Los Angeles Rams.

headline.print_headline: Jared Goff Leads Rams' Rookies Into Training Camp
